## SavourEase

*SavourEase* is a *Savouries Business Website & Mobile Application* designed to enhance service delivery, order management, and inventory control for local savoury businesses.  
The platform allows customers to easily browse, order, and pay for savoury products, while giving administrators the tools to manage orders, update inventory, and track business performance â€” all in one place.

---

## ğŸŒ Project Overview

*SavourEase* aims to:
- Provide customers with a *user-friendly online ordering experience* via web and mobile.
- Enable business owners to *manage inventory, update product listings, and monitor orders* efficiently.
- Deliver real-time updates on *order status* and *delivery tracking*.
- Support *secure online payments* and reliable data handling through Azure integration.

